## Catalog submission

This PR proposes adding `release-manager`, a Hermes Agent profile distribution.

## User value

Reviews release readiness and changelog discipline for Hermes profile repositories.

## Install

```bash
hermes profile install https://github.com/acme/release-manager --alias
```

## Safety and maintenance notes

- Source: https://github.com/acme/release-manager
- Version: 0.1.0
- License: MIT
- Safety: Does not include runtime state, secrets, memories, sessions, or private user data. Validate before publishing with `make validate`.
- I checked this target catalog's contribution rules before submitting.
- This entry does not claim unofficial affiliations, audits, support channels, or production guarantees.
